      "role": "user",
      "content": "but what if i don't want to move forward? moving forward feels like a betrayal. like i'm just pretending he didn't happen. honestly, the thought of a \"life for myself\" just sounds exhausting. it feels like i've already finished my story, and i'm just reading the same empty pages over and over again. it's so much more peaceful to just... let go of the effort.",
